---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SafeImage from "../../components/SafeImage.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="About Rocco" description="Meet Rocco the Repair Guy - 20+ years of fixing problems, building trust, and helping neighbors.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Rocco, the Repair Guy</h1>
      <p class="lede">Fixing problems. Building trust. Helping neighbors.</p>
        <SafeImage
      src="/assets/rocco/rocco-card.png"
      alt="Rocco, the Repair Guy"
      width={280}
      height={280}
      class="rocco-about-img"
    />
</div>
  </section>
  <section class="container" style="padding:40px 20px 64px">
    <p>Rocco's been fixing, building, and problem-solving for over 20 years. He knows the right questions to ask, the scams to avoid, and how to help you get the job done right &mdash; the first time. He's your go-to guide for finding trusted local pros.</p>
    <h2>What Rocco's about</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><h3>Trustworthy</h3><p>Straight shooter. Does what he says.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Hardworking</h3><p>Experienced. Gets it done.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h3>Neighborly</h3><p>Treats your home like his own.</p></div>
    </div>
    <blockquote class="disclaimer" style="margin-top:24px">
      "Good work ain't cheap, cheap work ain't good. Let's get it done right." &mdash; Rocco
    </blockquote>
    <p class="soft-note" style="margin-top:16px">Rocco is an AI guide. He equips you with understanding and the right questions &mdash; he never diagnoses and never replaces a licensed professional.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
